 
Compiling and downloading code for the mega...

The code running on the mega uses the arduino libraries for convenience.

In order to compile and download them, use the command line arduino
tool - arduino-cli.

For instance,
 arduino-cli compile --fqbn arduino:avr:mega mega.ino
 arduino-cli upload --port /dev/ttyACM0 --fqbn arduino:avr:mega .
 
or
 arduino-cli compile --fqbn arduino:avr:mega -v --clean mega.ino
